Interface NodeBuilderFactory<T extends NodeBuilder,S extends Activity>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20ConvergingComplexGatewayNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20ConvergingExclusiveGatewayNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20ConvergingParallelGatewayNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20DecisionUserTaskNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20DivergingComplexGatewayNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20DivergingExclusiveGatewayNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20DivergingParallelGatewayNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20ExitNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20LoopDecisionUserTaskNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20NodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20ScriptTaskNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20ServiceTaskNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20SignalEventNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20SubProcessNodeBuilderFactory, Bpmn20UserTaskNodeBuilderFactory

    public interface NodeBuilderFactory<T extends NodeBuilder,S extends Activity>
    Interface for all NodeBuilderFactory subclasses. Each NodeBuilder subclass must have a corresponding NodeBuilderFactory Each notation system (BPMN20 or JPDL) will have its own set of NodeBuilderFactory classes T is the type of NodeBuilder returned by the factory S is the type of Activity that this NodeBuilder will use as its input.
    Author:
    JKRANES
